reviewText:
for 7$ its a scam but now for 1,39 is pretty good ( when you hold in mind that this is a mobile port)

controlls with pad is horrible but with keyboard everything is fine.

another question to codemasters why is the android version of this game 2,56 regular price and PC 6,99 for the same game? and why u cant bring just an collection on steam with all the cmr games for good price?  questions over questions but at the end its  a good game when its on sale

I don't understand why this game has negative reviews.

pros:
- achievements;
- trading cards;
- has a single player cool campaign;

cons:
- the graphics quality (which are not that bad in the end);

I can easily recommend it !
